<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Free Word Counter Tool - Count Words Online</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*{box-sizing:border-box;}
body{
background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #1e3a8a 0%, #0a0f14 60%);
min-height:100vh;
padding:20px;
font-family:'Poppins', sans-serif;
color:#fff;
}
.container{max-width:950px; margin:0 auto;}

/* HERO */
.hero{
text-align:center;
padding:40px 20px;
}
.hero h1{
font-size:36px;
background: linear-gradient(90deg, #60a5fa, #a78bfa, #f472b6);
-webkit-background-clip: text;
-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
font-weight:700;
margin-bottom:10px;
}
.hero p{color:#94a3b8; font-size:16px;}

/* COUNTER BOX */
.counter-box{
background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
border-radius:24px;
padding:30px;
box-shadow: 0 25px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
margin-bottom:30px;
animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease;
}
@keyframes fadeIn{from{opacity:0; transform:translateY(20px);} to{opacity:1; transform:translateY(0);}}

textarea{
width:100%;
height:300px;
background: rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
border:2px solid #334155;
border-radius:18px;
padding:20px;
color:#fff;
font-size:16px;
resize:none;
outline:none;
transition: all 0.3s ease;
}
textarea:focus{
border-color:#6366f1;
box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(99,102,241,0.4);
}

/* STATS CARDS */
.stats{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
gap:18px;
margin:25px 0;
}
@media(min-width:700px){
.stats{grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);}
}
.stat-box{
background: linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(99,102,241,0.15), rgba(139,92,246,0.15));
padding:20px;
border-radius:18px;
text-align:center;
border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
transition: all 0.4s ease;
cursor:default;
}
.stat-box:hover{
transform: translateY(-6px) scale(1.03);
border-color:#8b5cf6;
box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(139,92,246,0.3);
}
.stat-box .icon{font-size:28px; margin-bottom:8px;}
.stat-box h3{
font-size:28px;
background: linear-gradient(90deg, #8b5cf6, #ec4899);
-webkit-background-clip: text;
-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
font-weight:700;
}
.stat-box p{
font-size:13px;
color:#cbd5e1;
font-weight:500;
margin-top:4px;
}

.btn-clear{
background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ef4444, #f97316);
color:#fff;
border:none;
padding:15px 25px;
border-radius:16px;
font-weight:600;
cursor:pointer;
width:100%;
font-size:16px;
transition: all 0.3s ease;
}
.btn-clear:hover{
transform: translateY(-3px);
box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(239,68,68,0.5);
}

/* SECTION */
.section{
background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
border-radius:24px;
padding:35px;
margin-bottom:30px;
}
.section h2{
font-size:24px;
margin-bottom:18px;
background: linear-gradient(90deg, #60a5fa, #a78bfa);
-webkit-background-clip: text;
-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
}
.section p, .section li{color:#cbd5e1; line-height:1.8; margin-bottom:10px;}
.section ul{padding-left:20px;}

.faq-item{
border-bottom:1px solid #334155;
padding:18px 0;
}
.faq-item:last-child{border:none;}
.faq-item h3{
font-size:17px;
margin-bottom:8px;
color:#a78bfa;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">

<!-- HERO -->
<div class="hero">
<div style="font-size:60px; margin-bottom:10px;">📝</div>
<h1>Free Word Counter Tool</h1>
<p>Instantly count words, characters, sentences. 100% Free & No Signup</p>
</div>

<!-- COUNTER TOOL -->
<div class="counter-box">
<textarea id="textInput" placeholder="Start typing or paste your text here..."></textarea>
<div class="stats">
<div class="stat-box">
<div class="icon">📄</div>
<h3 id="words">0</h3>
<p>Total Words</p>
</div>
<div class="stat-box">
<div class="icon">🔤</div>
<h3 id="chars">0</h3>
<p>Characters</p>
</div>
<div class="stat-box">
<div class="icon">📝</div>
<h3 id="sentences">0</h3>
<p>Sentences</p>
</div>
<div class="stat-box">
<div class="icon">📚</div>
<h3 id="paragraphs">0</h3>
<p>Paragraphs</p>
</div>
</div>
<button class="btn-clear" onclick="clearAll()">🗑️ Clear All Text</button>
</div>

<!-- HOW TO USE -->
<div class="section">
<h2>How To Use</h2>
<ul>
<li><b>Step 1:</b> Uporer box e tomar content likho ba paste koro</li>
<li><b>Step 2:</b> Real-time e sob count auto update hobe</li>
<li><b>Step 3:</b> Pro features unlock korte "Watch Ad" option use koro</li>
<li><b>Step 4:</b> "Clear All" diye notun kore suru koro</li>
</ul>
</div>

<!-- FEATURES -->
<div class="section">
<h2>Why Use Our Tool?</h2>
<ul>
<li>🚀 <b>Lightning Fast</b> - 1 sec eo lagbe na</li>
<li>🎨 <b>Beautiful UI</b> - Dekhte premium lagbe</li>
<li>📱 <b>100% Responsive</b> - Mobile e darun kaj kore</li>
<li>🔒 <b>Privacy First</b> - Tomar data kothao save hoyna</li>
</ul>
</div>

<!-- FAQ -->
<div class="section">
<h2>FAQ</h2>
<div class="faq-item">
<h3>Q1. Eta ki sotti free?</h3>
<p>Haan 100% free. Pro unlock korte chaile 1ta ad dekhlei 1 ghonta free pabe.</p>
</div>
<div class="faq-item">
<h3>Q2. Koto boro text support kore?</h3>
<p>Unlimited. 50,000 word er article o paste korte paro, kono problem nei.</p>
</div>
<div class="faq-item">
<h3>Q3. Pro te ki thakbe?</h3>
<p>Keyword Density, Reading Time, PDF Export, Ads Free r onek kichu.</p>
</div>
</div>

</div>

<script>
function countWords(){
let text = document.getElementById('textInput').value;
document.getElementById('words').innerText = text.trim() ? text.trim().split(/\s+/).length : 0;
document.getElementById('chars').innerText = text.length;
document.getElementById('sentences').innerText = text.split(/[.!?]+/).filter(Boolean).length;
document.getElementById('paragraphs').innerText = text.split(/\n\s*\n/).filter(Boolean).length;
}
function clearAll(){
document.getElementById('textInput').value='';
countWords();
}
document.getElementById('textInput').addEventListener('input', countWords);
</script>

</body>
</html>
